snippet.title: Spellsworn - Gameplay Trailer (Free-to-Play)
snippet.description:
A new trailer for in honor of our visit to Gamescom 2017!
Spellsworn is a game based on the warlock mod for Warcraft III, and it's what we like to call "wizard duels with sumo-wrestling rules".
It is currently on Steam Early Access!
http://store.steampowered.com/app/360...

Check it out if you're interested! Or maybe stop by our homepage.
http://www.spellsworn.com
...and social media
www.facebook.com/frogsongstudios
https://twitter.com/FrogsongStudios

Thanks for looking in!
/Frogsong Studios
